title: TPB Music Video's For Shania's Fans
description:
TV Quality, 4.2GB This DVD was made by a SUPER SHANIA FAN, who I will call M/s M who lived in Holland for a 2nd Super Shania Fan, who lived in Shania's Home town of Timmins for over 6 years as he had a Girl Friend there for a bit. 

Sadly the Shania Twain Centre was demolished to make way for a giant open mine, but I am sure Shania is enjoying her life away from the spotlight now and we will always have these super memories. 

Many of you may of met Shania in person, I know I did. So to Quote her "Be Careful what you wish for, for your wish may even come true." Fame never changed Shania, and I am sure the passage of Time has never stopped you still being a Shania Twain Fan, or being the best person you can.

I do hope you get as much pleasure watching these again as I did the first time I played back this home made DVD. 

This will play on all computer platforms which can use DVD playback software or the FREE VLC Media Player. PAL Region Free. Thank you Shania for the Music, the Memories and the Great Times and thank you fellow Shania Fan's, you were and still are, very special people.
